creator: HoteLux
descriptionHtml:
HoteLux is a membership-based luxury hotel reservation app with instant booking confirmation.
As a HoteLux member, you will be able to enjoy member exclusive benefits and promotions, including:
• Daily breakfasts
• Up to USD 100 hotel dining / spa credit
• Complimentary room upgrade (subject to availability)
• Double dip on points – earn both hotel loyalty program and HoteLux points
• Early check-in & late check-out (subject to availability)
• Welcome amenities
• Pay upon check-in and flexible cancellation policy

With a portfolio of globally acclaimed luxury hotel groups, HoteLux is a member of their exclusive and invite-only luxury agent programs such as:
• Four Seasons Preferred Partner
• Shangri-la The Luxury Circle
• Hyatt Privé
• Marriott STARS & Luminous
• Mandarin Oriental Fan Club
• VITA by The Leading Hotels of the World
• The Peninsula PenClub
• Rosewood Elite
• Hilton Impresario
• The IHG Luxury & Lifestyle
descriptionShort: A membership-based luxury hotel reservation app connecting 4,000+ luxury hotels

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Optimized the currency unit and points earning form;
Fix known issues.

title: HoteLux: Stay Better

creator: HoteLux
descriptionHtml:
HoteLux is a membership-based luxury hotel reservation app with instant booking confirmation.
As a HoteLux member, you will be able to enjoy member exclusive benefits and promotions, including:
• Daily breakfasts
• Up to USD 200 hotel dining / spa credit
• Complimentary room upgrade (subject to availability)
• Double dip on points – earn both hotel loyalty program and HoteLux points
• Early check-in & late check-out (subject to availability)
• Welcome amenities
• Pay upon check-in and flexible cancellation policy

With a portfolio of globally acclaimed luxury hotel groups, HoteLux is a member of their exclusive and invite-only luxury agent programs such as:
• Four Seasons Preferred Partner
• Shangri-la The Luxury Circle
• Hyatt Privé
• Marriott STARS & Luminous
• Mandarin Oriental Fan Club
• VITA by The Leading Hotels of the World
• The Peninsula PenClub
• Rosewood Elite
• Hilton Impresario
• The IHG Luxury & Lifestyle
descriptionShort: Book global luxury hotels with unprecedented benefits

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Immerse yourself in the timeless charm of a Japanese Ryokan, now available on our app. Book your stay and enjoy exclusive HoteLux Benefits such as 10,000 JPY Property Credit, Complimentary Room Upgrade, Early Check-in/Late Check-out, and more!
*HoteLux Benefits very per property.

We also offering a special promotion to our members below:
Get a complimentary 3-month membership at the corresponding level for every completed night, up to 12 months.
